{"tid":1533600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再留守","createTime":"2019-09-02T18:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T19:27:47.000Z","uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c2858a567067f3e3d4ee882ab89c766a4424a6c","tid":1533600,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:14:43.000Z","msg":"講都講到口臭，留守係無意思。留守只會有兩個下場：<br />\n1. 清場<br />\n2. 佢行行企企兇下你﹑用下水炮車射濕幾件﹑開槍射低幾件再清你場<br />\n最後只會得一個結果，就係手足受傷﹑被捕，而係無人想見到嘅。<br />\n<br />\n所以，而家可以做嘅：<br />\n1. hit &amp; <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">RUN</span></strong> 記得RUN 記得RUN 記得RUN！講緊可以照起路障，但成功塞到路就要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">RUN</span></strong>，留喺度又loop返上面所講畀人清<br />\n<br />\n2. 撚狗。隔離有個post都有講，圍狗屋係無用，但可以喺狗屋附近行行企企咁，佢哋出嚟就即散水，到佢哋入返狗屋又出返嚟。<br />\n詳情可以參考返隔離post：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1476517/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1476517/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 亦都係今次開post最主要想集思廣益嘅目的：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點樣可以聚到一班可靠嘅勇武出嚟反擊？</span></strong> 好老實，新屋嶺強姦我唔希望係真，但手足畀狗咬﹑到女手足畀狗非禮<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">﹙特別係今日睇唐詩勁個post睇到好撚嬲，內容大概係話有男狗喺太子搜女仔身，不繼摸佢上面，仲用手磨擦佢下面幾十秒，話「點知你會唔會收埋係呢啲地方，搜清楚啲好」，仲細細聲講左句好舒服喎<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cherryyycc/posts/1352601708239476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcherryyycc%2Fposts%2F1352601708239476&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=6e5c4a45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cherryyycc/posts/1352601708239476</a>﹚</span>，我哋完全無辦法可以反抗到，現行制度根本係無辦法可以整治到啲狗。明刀明槍我哋一定打輸，所以想大家集思廣益，點樣可以首先聚到班可靠嘅勇武出嚟做黑暗騎士？"},{"pid":"39b2e92fb25180d8d6061f3615a7e35512755c52","tid":1533600,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:19:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b705a4d29f547c1e01477211e03862213c7f704","tid":1533600,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=524e0266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外就係有個DSE支援服務。<br />\n<br />\n形式係以分科細谷你問我答為主，亦有提供簡單練習同改文服務。同學亦可以問升學選科等問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如有同學有需要，請聯絡：<br />\nTG: mama612 <br />\nTG: UuuncleK<br />\n(暫時有足夠Tutor所以暫不接受更多tutor)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1006375f5055f230750634b1c40b00738101f3","tid":1533600,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fada54b013036f2cfaaf34721172258de0863a6e","tid":1533600,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:27:47.000Z","msg":"［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/